metadata.name: Faceless Void
metadata.description:
Circle Studio is proud to present Faceless Void, the first of 7 collectible models that premiered in the Opening Ceremony of the Dota 2 Kuala Lumpur Major in 2018 that wow-ed Dota 2 fans across the globe. 

Get locked in time as you watch Faceless Void come to life in our opening ceremony feature; “First Blood”. More unique characters from “First Blood” will gradually be released and are limited to one copy each!

This timeless remastered version of Faceless Void comes equipped with our in-house designed armor and weapon. 

Character : Faceless Void
Dimensions : 1080px x 1080px
Format : Mp4

Check out the video here:
https://vimeo.com/406049552
